        p.text &OpenCurlyQuote;Talking of shirts&comma;&rsquor; I said&comma; &OpenCurlyQuote;have those mauve ones I ordered arrived yet&quest;&rsquor;
        p.text &OpenCurlyQuote;Yes&comma; sir&period; I sent them back&period;&rsquor;
        p.text &OpenCurlyQuote;Sent them back&quest;&rsquor;
        p.text &OpenCurlyQuote;Yes&comma; sir&period; They would not have become you&period;&rsquor;
        p.text
          | Well&comma; I must say I&rsquor;d thought fairly highly of those shirtings&comma; but I bowed to superior knowledge&period; Weak&quest; I don&rsquor;t know&period; Most fellows&comma; no doubt&comma; are all for having their valets confine their activities to creasing trousers and what not without trying to run the home&semi; but it&rsquor;s different with Jeeves&period; Right from the first day he come to me&comma; I have looked on him as a sort of guide&comma; philosopher and friend&period;
        p.text
