        p.text &OpenCurlyQuote;Just as you say&period; Who is she&quest; Tell me all&period;&rsquor;
        p.text
          | For I realized now that poor old Bingo was going through it once again&period; Ever since I have known him &ndash; and we were at school together &ndash; he has been perpetually falling in love with someone&comma; generally in the spring&comma; which seems to act on him like magic&period; At school he had the finest collection of actresses&rsquor; photographs of anyone of this time&semi; and at Oxford his romantic nature was a byword&period;
